### Movie CRUD

# @name createMovie
POST http://localhost:5000/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Inception",
  "description": "A thief who steals corporate secrets through the use of dream-sharing technology.",
  "year": 2010
}

### Get all movies
GET http://localhost:5000/movies

### Get single movie (replace with actual ID from createMovie response)
GET http://localhost:5000/movies/ID_HERE

### Update movie (replace with actual ID)
PUT http://localhost:5000/movies/ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Inception (Updated)",
  "year": 2011
}

### Delete movie (replace with actual ID)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/movies/ID_HERE

---

### Review CRUD

# @name addReview
POST http://localhost:5000/movies/ID_HERE/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user": "John Doe",
  "content": "Mind-blowing movie! Loved the concept.",
  "rating": 9
}

### Get reviews for a movie
GET http://localhost:5000/movies/ID_HERE/reviews

### Update a review (replace with actual review ID)
PUT http://localhost:5000/reviews/ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Still great on the second watch!",
  "rating": 10
}

### Delete a review (replace with actual review ID)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/reviews/ID_HERE
